{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a Shopify subscription page for Unchained Coffee that replicates the format and functional structure of the Onyx Coffee Lab subscription page.
    
    The page must include only the following core sections, in this exact logical order:
    
    1. Coffee Selection
    
    Section title: Choose Your Coffee
    
    Display selectable coffee options (cards or list).
    
    Each option should support image, coffee name, and short description.
    
    Selection must dynamically affect the subscription product.
    
    2. Delivery Quantity Selection
    
    Section title: Choose Your Bag Size
    
    Provide variant options:
    
    250 g
    
    1 kg
    
    This selection must update pricing dynamically.
    
    3. Subscription Type
    
    Create two clear subscription modes using tabs, toggles, or segmented controls:
    
    Option A: Subscribe by Frequency
    
    Section label: Subscribe on a Schedule
    
    Frequency options:
    
    Weekly
    
    Every 2 weeks
    
    Monthly
    
    Include microcopy explaining flexibility (skip, pause, cancel).
    
    Option B: Subscribe by Usage
    
    Section label: Subscribe by Usage
    
    Short explanatory text describing automatic reorders based on usage.
    
    Include placeholder for future smart-usage integration.
    
    4. Gift Subscription
    
    Section title: This Is a Gift
    
    Allow users to select gift subscriptions based on number of shipments:
    
    3 shipments
    
    6 shipments
    
    12 shipments
    
    Gift option should function independently from frequency subscriptions.
    
    5. Primary Call to Action
    
    Prominent Add to Cart / Subscribe button.
    
    Button text should dynamically reflect subscription type selection.
    
    Button must remain visible or sticky as user scrolls.
    
    Design & UX Rules
    
    Clean, minimalist layout.
    
    Clear section separation.
    
    Large readable typography.
    
    Mobile-first responsive design.
    
    Avoid unnecessary marketing sections or long copy.
    
    Output Requirements
    
    Generate final page layout and section structure suitable for Shopify.
    
    Include headings, placeholder copy, and variant logic descriptions.
    
    Use neutral placeholder text that can later be customized to Unchained tone.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-subscription-page-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .ai-subscription-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid {{ block.settings.divider_color }};
  }

  .ai-subscription-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .ai-subscription-section-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.section_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-subscription-section-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: {{ block.settings.secondary_text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ai-coffee-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ai-coffee-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    background: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
  }

